In FY2017, a key priority for SGX was

to enhante the robustness of our technological and crisis management infrastructure so as to ensure market continuity. In consultation with the Monetary Authority of Singapore (MAS), SGX formed a Securities Industry Working Group (IWG) in November 2016 to spearhead initiatives to improve operational resilience of the market.

Demonstrating our resolve to minimise the adverse impact from a market disruption, SGX agreed to adopt all recommendations proposed by
